    "title": "Mid-Level Fleet Manager at FM Logistic India",
    "description": "FM Logistic India invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Fleet Manager at our Chennai location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout FM Logistic India:\nFM Logistic India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Learning & development budget\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Chennai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with FM Logistic India!",
